hopobject.body: I'd like to speak to someone about a mortgage how long after drinking can i take viagra But Souza's real passion is the Atlantic bushmaster, one of the most poisonous snakes in the western hemisphere. Thick-bodied and up to 3m long, these majestic creatures have distinctive orange and black markings and heat-seeking sensors under the eyes that allow them to lock on to warm-blooded mammals. A human can die within an hour of being bitten unless they receive the right anti-venom injection.
